column4: hey can i get some help it says one of my packages has unmet dependencies
hey im selling this computer tomorrow and the package manager is throwin me an error ive never seen can i PLEASEget some help

when i try to update with the package manager it says an error occoured please run apt-get to see whats wrong the error message was 'error: brokencount>0 this usually means that your installed packages have unmet dependencies
